I was looking for a star wars challenge and the only one I found is one from 2017 so I'm gonna make a new easier one to find

 

So basically to complete the requirements to look like a star wars craft in my book it must have a: class,some weapons(if needed),star warsesqe

Also this is not for 1 to 1 replicas I'm saying it must be a star wars like ship anyways have fun!

 

(Winner gets free snacks lol)
